            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely dice your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Once the meatballs have browned, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1720777127679-x200.jpg",
