            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the meatballs are cooking, add your<strong> bulgur wheat</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> (the same as you would for pasta)</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 7-9 min or until tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain and return to the pot</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1720777147183-x200.jpg",
