            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong> then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine your <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>in a large bowl – this is your <strong>salad dressing</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>salad </strong>to the dressing and toss – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1720777152618-x200.jpg",
