    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Moroccan-style meatballs</strong> with the <strong>bulgur wheat </strong>and <strong>dressed salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Dollop over your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>and sprinkle over your <strong>3 seed mix</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
